{"tid":1547084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個ex警犬結婚 佢請我去","createTime":"2019-09-06T14:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T14:53:22.000Z","uid":161163,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"63a59e2fbb4640265c31c9cc1e9efcde5658e2c5","tid":1547084,"uid":161163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"我有個ex係隻警🐶<br />\n2年前 佢同左第三者一齊之後飛左我<br />\n有一日 佢打比我話要結婚 問我去唔去<br />\n我真係嬲到喊 你結咪結同我講做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我咪扮野話祝福佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到佢結婚嗰日 我打扮得好靚去到佢結婚個酒店<br />\n嗰陣佢同佢老婆企埋一齊影緊相<br />\n我就行埋佢 同佢地講恭喜<br />\n然後喺佢耳邊同佢講左句 你都有今日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣佢老婆見到我咁 佢個樣已經西西地<br />\n我再用懶細聲但係可以比佢老婆聽到嘅聲量同佢講左句 好掛住你 後晚見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢聽到之後呆左 到佢反應過嚟屌9我嗰陣 我已經走左去<br />\n<br />\n其實我有個姐妹仲癡線<br />\n佢有個ex又係警犬 又係一腳踏兩船飛左佢<br />\n佢癲線到走去人地結婚教堂講 我反對！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲去酒樓發癲話好愛佢做乜離開佢 搞串哂人地party<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我都係痴線西 但係我就好道德嘅<br />\n我姐妹做嗰啲我真係做唔出<br />\n我就奉勸你地唔好咁做呀<br />\n一生人一次嘅婚禮真係好重要 <br />\n我都後悔嗰陣講左嗰句野 可以嘅話我會講得激啲<br />\n不過你地千奇唔好搞到人個婚禮呀知未 <br />\n真係唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af4929d96b5d76526678533bd5a00cdcff798b4","tid":1547084,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b40fb9b0c84585d9db0bd48175c04fb3865df09f","tid":1547084,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:19:45.000Z","msg":"冇圖冇地點冇名 想點"},{"pid":"6541be3f529c3354110538313dd558e835fb96b9","tid":1547084,"uid":290761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vAmVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vAmVU.jpg&h=305434b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門區校友街坊們過黎幫手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed464ec50c7dbb2b2b74c601d1c6195b63e42ce","tid":1547084,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"},{"pid":"bafd6982bfadf44963684e41bdc2b92cca30a6c9","tid":1547084,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"我代你去"},{"pid":"4778ab19521b8fd910b214bc659ae2dcd6d584c6","tid":1547084,"uid":6111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T14:49:15.000Z","msg":"講時間地點出黎就會有人去"},{"pid":"1d92aca6d3c41740487f881f49033029e94